{ Black is lost here with best play, but which move gives black some hope with a tempting trap? }
1... hxg5+ { Excellent! Black is still lost but white is in check and if the king captures on g5 then the game is drawn. } 2. Kxg5 Kxa2 3. h6 Kb1 (3... a3 { This also works but play Kb1 for the continuation. }) 4. h7 a3 5. h8=Q a2 { And black will either promote and exchange or threaten a stalemate on a1 which wouldn't be possible if the g pawn were still on the board. } *


