[FEN "8/1pp5/1p4p1/3Pp1k1/P3P2p/5K2/1P3P1P/8 b - - 0 2"]
[SetUp "1"]
[UTCDate "2023.02.12"]
[UTCTime "16:01:52"]
[ChapterMode "gamebook"]

{ White has just thrown away the win after a4?? Black to play and draw. }
2... Kh5 { Excellent! Black creates a path for the g pawn in order to set up a fortress. } 3. b4 b5 { Excellent! This prevents any breakthroughs on the queenside. } 4. axb5 b6 { Excellent! Now white's queenside is frozen. } 5. h3 g5 6. Kg2 g4 7. f4 gxf3+ 8. Kxf3 Kg5 { And there is no way for white to make progress. } *


