[ChapterMode "gamebook"]

{ White must be extremely careful here. White to play and win. }
1. Kg2 (1. Kg1 { This also works but play Kg2 for the continuation. }) 1... Kf6 2. Kf2 { Excellent! The important opposition is that on the f file. } 2... Ke5 3. Ke3 *


