[ChapterMode "gamebook"]

{ White to play and win. }
1. d5 { Excellent! The only move. The pawn sacrifices itself to block the black king's path. } (1. a4 { This is too hasty. Now black can draw with Ke4! }) 1... exd5 2. a4 { Playing a4 didn't work, but now with the extra tempo the black king can't stop it. } 2... Ke4 3. a5 Kd4 4. a6 *


