{ White's king is tied to the connected passed pawns on the kingside, but black is also immobile. White to play and win. }
1. Kh3 { Excellent! Black is now in zugzwang. } (1. Kf3 { This also works but makes less sense than Kh3. }) 1... g4+ 2. Kxg4 h3 3. Kxh3 { And black's king must leave the square of the a pawn. } *


