{ White to play and win. }
1. f6 { An incredible sacrifice! It's difficult to see but this creates a barrier that prevents the black king from catching white's a pawn. } 1... gxf6 2. Kxg2 Kg5 3. a4 (3. a3 { This also works but play a4 for the continuation. }) 3... bxa3 4. bxa3 Kf5 5. a4 { And now the a pawn races to promotion. } *


