{ White to play and draw. }
1. g4+ { Excellent! White sacrifices a pawn in order to clear the way for its king to reach the c pawn. } 1... Kxg4 2. Kg6 c5 3. h4 { Now if black captures the a pawn then white can reach the c pawn and if black pushes the c pawn then white also promotes the h pawn. } (3. h3+ { This also works but play h4 for the continuation. }) *


